          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/828.-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel 2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[4]</span>&nbsp;<strong>shallots</strong>&nbsp;(you'll use the rest later!)&nbsp;and all of the <strong>garlic&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>Peel the <strong>ginger</strong> (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon)</p>\r\n<p>Cut the stalks off the <strong>coriander</strong>&nbsp;and set the leaves aside for later &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Cut the stalk off of the <strong>red&nbsp;chilli<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/828.-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/828.-step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/828.-step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/828.-step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/828.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>shallot</strong>, <strong>garlic</strong>, <strong>ginger</strong>, <strong>coriander stalks</strong>, <strong>chilli </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)&nbsp;and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span><strong>&nbsp;vegetable oil&nbsp;</strong>to a <strong>food processor</strong> and blitz the lot to a coarse paste&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you don't have a food processor, just chop everything together finely&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
